parameters.name: L_star
parameters.description: Lstar - Roederer's generalized L-shell parameter. Computed for 90deg. particles using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: L
parameters.description: ---> L - McIlwain's L-shell parameter. Computed for 90deg. particles using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: I
parameters.description: ---> I - Integral invariant. Computed for 90deg. particles using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: B_Calc
parameters.description: ---> B_Calc - Magnitude of computed model field at the S/C. Computed using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: B_Eq
parameters.description: ---> B_Eq - Magnitude of computed model field at the Minimum-|B| point along the field line threading the S/C. Computed using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: MLT
parameters.description: ---> MLT - Eccentric Dipole Magnetic Local Time. Computed using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: MLAT
parameters.description: ---> MLAT - Eccentric Dipole Magnetic Latitude. Computed using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: Position
parameters.description: ---> Position - Geocentric Geocentric position in Re.

parameters.name: LstarVsAlpha
parameters.description: ---> LstarVsAlpha - Roederer's generalized L-shell parameter. Pitch angle depenedent (pitch angles are local pitch angles). Computed using OP77Q external field and IGRF internal field.

parameters.name: LstarVsAlpha_Alpha
parameters.description: ---> Alpha values for LstarVsAlpha variable. I.e., they are the local pitch angles that L* is computed for in LstarVsAlpha. Units are degrees.
